data.description: Nestled in the heart of Midlothian, this stunning 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom home is a true masterpiece of modern living. Situated on a spacious lot adjacent to a lush greenbelt. The 2023 renovations have elevated this residence to unparalleled levels of sophistication and comfort. Upon entering, the vaulted ceilings create an open and airy ambiance, accentuating the sense of space throughout. The new windows, adorned with a lifetime warranty, flood the interiors with natural light, seamlessly merging the indoors with the picturesque outdoors. The home boasts new quartz countertops throughout, as well as the addition of shutters and shiplap walls that add a touch of contemporary charm. Step outside into your private oasis, where a gunite pool and hot tub await, inviting you to relax and unwind. Perfect for entertaining or enjoying a quiet evening under the stars. Close proximity to schools ensures convenience for families, while the greenbelt offers a sense of serenity and privacy.
